title: Fearless Chef S01E01 Bolivia HDTV.x264-SQUEAK
description:
The ten part travel adventure series Fearless Chef is a one of a kind high adrenaline adventure food programme that promises to pack a riveting punch as Chef Kiran Jethwa, food adventurer and global gastronaut, traverses the globe showcasing fascinating ingredients and the extreme methods of harvesting. His journey takes him from Africa to Latin America, and across Asia. He meets with extraordinary people and turns their hard earned harvest into mouth-watering meals. When it comes to food, the tougher the challenge, the better the taste will be. Travel around the globe and watch Kiran create some amazing, delicious, locally inspired dishes.
